                                    </mod>
                                 </p>
                              </content>
                           </alinea>
                        </point>
                        <point>
                           <num>(c)</num>
                           <alinea>
                              <content>
                                 <p>in Part 1, in section &apos;UNITED KINGDOM&apos; the first sentence is replaced by the following:</p>
                              </content>
                           </alinea>
                           <alinea>
                              <content>
                                 <p>
                                    <mod>
                                       <quotedStructure startQuote="" endQuote="">
                                          <alinea>
                                             <content>
                                                <p>&apos;All applications for retirement pension, state pension pursuant to Part 1 of the Pensions Act 2014, widows&apos; and bereavement benefits, with the exception of those for which during a tax year beginning on or after 6 April 1975:&apos;;</p>
                                             </content>
                                          </alinea>
